--step-1
Go to Page Designer -> Pre-Rendering -> Before Header.

Right-click and select Create Process.

Name: Initialize Requisition Collection.
--pl/sql code add
PL/SQL Code:
IF NOT APEX_COLLECTION.COLLECTION_EXISTS('REQ_ITEMS') THEN
    APEX_COLLECTION.CREATE_COLLECTION('REQ_ITEMS');
END IF;

--step-2
Region (Static Content)
Items:

P1_REQ_DATE: Date Picker (Default to SYSDATE).

P1_CREATE_BY: Select List (SQL Query based on users).

P1_PRIORITY: Select List (Static values: Low, Medium, High).
